name: CHEESED
description:
A game made in 48 for https://itch.io/jam/scorejam23, i know, it's weird but i did my best ;D

I made this game for a cousin, for his birthday, he's cool

CHEESED ia a game about a cheese trying to defend against hungry cats by throwing cheese at them

How to play WASD to Move, Mouse to Throw Cheese
